<paragraph blockId="7.[192,1441,1763,1915]" lastBlockId="8.[192,1441,195,891]" lastPageId="8" lastPageNumber="7" pageId="7" pageNumber="6">
<collectingCountry box="[192,418,1859,1883]" name="US Virgin Islands" pageId="7" pageNumber="6">US Virgin Islands</collectingCountry>
: St. Croix – 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[571,634,1859,1883]" pageId="7" pageNumber="6">1918</emphasis>
(Zwaluwenburg 1918 p. 6, misreported as “the changa”, the vernacular name bestowed on 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Latreille" baseAuthorityYear="1804" box="[584,746,1891,1915]" class="Insecta" family="Lathiceridae" genus="Scapteriscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="didactylus">
