<bibRefCitation author="Miskimen, G. W. &amp; R. M. Bond" box="[1082,1404,1891,1915]" pageId="7" pageNumber="6" pagination="1 - 114" refId="ref10376" refString="Miskimen, G. W., and R. M. Bond. 1970. The insect fauna of St. Croix, United StatesVirgin Islands. Scientific Survey of Porto Rico and the Virgin Islands (New York Academy of Sciences) 13: 1 - 114." type="journal article" year="1970">Miskimen and Bond 1970</bibRefCitation>
